> Theory and Practice, eds. D Z Sui, S Elwood, and M F Goodchild,
> 105–122. Berlin: Springer. doi:10.1007/978-94-007-4587-2_7.
> 
> Ioannidis, JPA. 2005. “Why Most Published Research Findings Are
